    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Safari 如何檢視網頁原始碼]]></title>
    <link href="http://mcyang.github.com/blog/2013/01/12/this-is-test-page/"/>
    <updated>2013-01-12T20:26:00+08:00</updated>
    <id>http://mcyang.github.com/blog/2013/01/12/this-is-test-page</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Octopress 全部設定完後開始要練習寫文章 , 為了秉持向全球 programmers 致敬的精神 ,</p>

<p>想當然爾就是開別人的 blog 檢視網頁原始碼參考一下囉!</p>

<p>但是... God! Safari 按右鍵怎麼找不到檢視原始碼呢?</p>

<p>請參考下列做法 :</p>

<blockquote><p>(1) Safari -> 偏好設定 -> 進階 -> 勾選 “在選單列中顯示開發人員選單“</p></blockquote>

<p><img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-pOq6zYgFMz8/UPI3Shtn_aI/AAAAAAAAAUg/0DeH16lxxwc/w980-h511-p-k/%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7%2B2013-01-13%2B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%258812.07.59.png"></p>

<blockquote><p>(2) Safari -> 開發人員 -> 顯示網頁原始碼 (或快速鍵 : option + command + a)</p></blockquote>

<p><img src="https://lh4.googleusercontent.com/-1NM9AVwTj9M/UPI3TZIQHMI/AAAAAAAAAUk/yqxo-UnokO8/w362-h225-n-k/%25E8%259E%25A2%25E5%25B9%2595%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E7%2585%25A7%2B2013-01-13%2B%25E4%25B8%258B%25E5%258D%258812.08.41.png"></p>
